>> Mom: I'm pretty excited, too.
"Win or don't win" is calling

12:25.579 --> 12:28.580
tonight.
All i have to do is answer one
question and I'll win a new

12:28.582 --> 12:32.016
microwave.
>> Gumball: What's wrong with
our microwave?

12:32.018 --> 12:36.554
[ Crackling ]
>> Darwin: Yeah, that makes
sense.

12:36.556 --> 12:39.624
>> Anais: Well, i can't wait to
watch "Daisy" tonight.
You're going to meet

12:39.626 --> 12:42.827
Sally the snake, aren't you,
Daisy?
"Yes, i am."

12:42.829 --> 12:48.166
[ All sigh ]
>> All: I can't wait till 8:00.
>> Gumball: Well, then i guess

12:48.168 --> 12:52.637
it's whoever gets to the remote
first!
[ Munching, slurping ]

12:56.075 --> 12:58.042
>> Mom: Aa-aa-aah!

13:00.613 --> 13:09.220
I've been up all night saving my
seat for...
[ Speaking Spanish ]

13:09.222 --> 13:13.191
And just to make sure no one
changes the channel, I've hidden
the remote!

13:13.193 --> 13:18.062
[ Laughing ]
[ Snoring ]
[ Indistinct shouting ]

13:18.064 --> 13:21.666
>> Anais: Can i please watch
"Daisy"?!
>> Together: No!

13:21.668 --> 13:25.103
[ Shouting continues ]
>> Darwin: This face was made
for TV!

13:25.105 --> 13:28.606
>> Mom: I don't want to grow a
third arm next time i make a cup
of coffee!

13:28.608 --> 13:34.646
>> Anais: I wish i had enough
money to buy my own remote!
>> Mom: Okay, well, you know

13:34.648 --> 13:39.083
what?
