>> Darwin: Wake up!

13:49.695 --> 13:54.632
[ Both sigh ]
>> Gumball: Wait a minute.
We don't need the remote.

13:54.634 --> 13:57.669
We can change the channel<i> on</i> the
TV.
>> Darwin: [ Gasps ]

13:57.671 --> 14:01.239
