man.

14:10.783 --> 14:16.120
>> Gumball: Ckk! Check, check.
[ Breathing heavily ]
Okay, control, I'm going in.

14:16.122 --> 14:19.324
Chk!
>> Darwin: Okay. Chk!
How you feeling?

14:19.326 --> 14:23.795
>> Gumball: Chk! To be honest,
I'm feeling pretty lazy.
>> Darwin: Chk! Keep going.

14:23.797 --> 14:27.732
You're doing great.
Chk!
>> Gumball: Something's

14:27.734 --> 14:31.936
