here before.

14:31.938 --> 14:36.140
I -- i...
I-i can't do it.
I'm gonna turn around!

14:36.142 --> 14:38.877
>> Darwin: No!
You've got to keep going!
You've passed the Christmas

14:38.879 --> 14:41.679
carpet stain.
There won't be enough willpower
to send you back.

14:41.681 --> 14:46.718
>> Gumball: Chk! Okay.
I'll try.
[ Grunting ]

14:46.720 --> 14:54.492
Gravity pulling me down!
I'm not gonna make it!
I...Can't...Be...

14:54.494 --> 14:57.795
Bothered!
[ Imitating static ]
>> Darwin: Abort the mission!

14:57.797 --> 15:04.802
I repeat -- abort the mission!
[ Echoing ] The mission.
>> Gumball: [ Groans, coughs ]

15:04.804 --> 15:07.906
I'm sorry, buddy, but it wasn't
possible.
[ Chuckles ]

15:07.908 --> 15:11.009
Now i know why remotes were
invented.
[ Chuckles, coughs ]

15:11.011 --> 15:15.013
>> Darwin: Here -- take this.
It'll make you feel better.
[ Chocolate bar snaps ]

15:15.015 --> 15:19.751
>> Dad: Did i hear chocolate?
>> Gumball: Ye-e-e-e-s.
And we'll give you some...

15:19.753 --> 15:22.186
When you tell us where the
remote is!
>> Dad: No! Never!

15:22.188 --> 15:26.724
>> Gumball: Oh, really?
Not even for the chocolate
choo-choo train?

15:26.726 --> 15:31.396
Ch-ch-ch-ch-choo-choo!
>> Dad: Aah!
>> Gumball: Ch-ch-ch-choo-choo!

15:31.398 --> 15:35.133
[ Telephone rings ]
>> Anais: I'll get it!
>> Gumball: Choo-choo!

15:35.135 --> 15:38.469
>> Dad: [ Crying ]
>> Mom: Anais, i need you to
tell me what brand the TV is.

15:38.471 --> 15:41.539
>> Anais: Okay. But does this
mean i can watch "Daisy"
tonight?

15:41.541 --> 15:44.842
>> Mom: No, it means you won't
be grounded for six months.
>> Anais: What?!

15:44.844 --> 15:48.479
But I'm 4!
That's like 1/8 of my life!
>> Mom: Then you don't want to

15:48.481 --> 15:50.882
