bedroom.
>> Anais: Ugh!

15:50.884 --> 15:55.787
Fine!
>> Gumball: Ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-
ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch...

15:55.789 --> 16:00.425
Ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-choo-choo!
>> Darwin: Bing-bong!
