>> Gumball: I got him!

16:50.944 --> 16:54.078
Get the remote!
>> Dad: Aah!
Where is it?!

16:54.080 --> 16:56.914
I've been sitting on it all day
long!
>> Gumball: There's only one

16:56.916 --> 17:00.551
