>> Darwin: Yeah! You!
Because it definitely wasn't me!

17:00.553 --> 17:03.821
Where did you put it?!
Where did you put it?!
Where did you put it?!

17:03.823 --> 17:08.326
>> Gumball: Dude, say it, don't
spray it!
>> Dad: Tell him where it is!

17:08.328 --> 17:13.965
Tell him where it is now!
>> Gumball: Chill, everybody!
I meant anais.

17:13.967 --> 17:18.336
It could only be anais.
>> Darwin: Oh.
'Cause we both want to watch the

17:18.338 --> 17:22.273
same thing.
