>> Dad: Get her!

17:22.275 --> 17:25.643
[ Footsteps approaching ]
>> Together: Where's the
remote?!

17:25.645 --> 17:28.479
>> Anais: What remote?
>> Gumball: Right!

17:35.654 --> 17:39.157
>> Anais: What are you doing?!
>> Gumball: Look! The scissors
she used to cut a hole in the

17:39.159 --> 17:41.459
